      "para_id": "Q000991.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(ii 7) In support of Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , Enlil installed Inana as his own helper , and both of them descended from the sky to his right and left ."
    }
